OL,3,GHighlands & Eilean Siar
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FMainly dry
OL,6,Fand a fine end to the day for many,
OL,7,Falthough cloudier around the west
OL,8,Fcoast. Patchy rain possible developing
OL,9,Fin the west overnight.
OL,10,
OL,11,CThursday:FSome drier and brighter
OL,12,Fspell around Inverness, Speyside and
OL,13,Fthe Black Isle, but mostly cloudy with
OL,14,Foutbreaks rain, the rain turning heavy
OL,15,Fand perhaps thundery at times.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
